{"tid":1264851,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我都知立會區會冇用，但都理由將議會拱手相讓","createTime":"2019-06-29T01:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T01:48:23.000Z","uid":116173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f37816b4b113474c10bfe80d6a706279196f6787","tid":1264851,"uid":116173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T01:37:42.000Z","msg":"[麻煩大家幫手share出去 7月2號就截止申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]<br />\n已經登記咗都要去查下啲資料啱唔啱<br />\n好多人都話冇咗選民記錄 大家都要check下 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fcheckvrstatus.htm&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6m0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=6fdd14db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm</a><br />\n或者打電話28911001 &gt; 1 &gt; 2去查 扮工時間9-6<br />\n<br />\n新登記<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgcnr.htm&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6m0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=a31cd451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n電子表格傳送門-&gt; <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6m0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=dae923cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n實體表格傳送門-&gt; 各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6m0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=ac0454bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n或公共屋邨辦事處<br />\n<a href=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201901%2F29%2FP2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6m0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=0957402d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf</a><br />\n或選舉事務處(香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓/九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓)<br />\n<br />\n交表<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6m0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=5198d82b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n如你持有有效的香港郵政或電子核證服務有限公司的電子核證（個人）證書 &lt;- 呢個基本冇人有，所以唔使試<br />\n<br />\n免費傳真方法 <br />\nHelloFax 免費黑白5張 / FAX.PLUS 免費黑白10張<br />\n<br />\n【教學】選民登記7月2日截止仲未搞？ 教你手機內3分鐘完成手續<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6m0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=dc40790c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a><br />\n[/麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]"},{"pid":"6780aed9cdca54aaeba5e8d78b3981478ff8f3bb","tid":1264851,"uid":116173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T01:42:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><